<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_35c06f06-a2af-4d1a-aa19-05110f4dc594" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>H2P3</sptc><title id="_2c94709e-430c-444d-8ef1-89faa29a1154">Rising damp</title><archive-num>2019: P2.2.3</archive-num><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/2049_0.7.0.xml" variation="NSW" variation-type="REPLACE">NSW REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/2048_0.6.0.xml" variation="SA" variation-type="REPLACE">SA REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_fc56b4d5-94d2-4057-a66e-58e863d60f3c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e125cdc5-1649-4ef9-918a-658baa3efb46">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Moisture from the ground must be prevented from causing—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_16e0f307-9ea9-40b8-9120-e86eb6a61613">unhealthy or dangerous conditions, or loss of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_67ae0c83-a607-42d2-81d0-c03f48f8b0d7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref> for occupants; and</li><li id="_19199f09-551c-4511-bd99-4ba5da416f72">undue dampness or deterioration of building elements.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_ee8207b1-66f1-4745-ba63-0432ddb4157c"><callout-type ncc-info-type="limitation"/><p>H2P3 does not apply to a Class 10 building where in the particular case there is no necessity for compliance.</p></callout></clause>